                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/1710" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0177</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8763 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从农民到产业工人的嬗变——德胜公司的员工再造</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Transmutation from Migrant Workers to Industrial Workers—— Rebirth of Employees in Tecsun (Suzho</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">徐世伟</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">德胜（苏州）洋楼有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">德胜；德胜员工守则；制度；农民工；员工再造</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Tecsun Homes；the employee manual of Tecsun Homes；system； migrant workers,  rebirth of employees</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">德胜公司制定的员工守则受到了外界的热捧。德胜虽是一家从事美制现代木（钢）结构住宅建造的规模不大的普通企业，但对员工的管理和再造却颇具特色。德胜的《德胜员工守则》，对企业运营的方方面面都进行了制度化详细规定，公司完全依靠制度进行管理，任何工作事务，都能够依据守则的规定进行处理，这些规定朴素而直白，内化为员工的行为，体现了德胜管理理念，德胜希冀把农民再造为真正的产业工人。在德胜，员工只要努力工作,就能确保衣食无忧，有福利保障，获得做人的尊严；员工的任何工作都必须按照设定的程序进行，正是对程序的执着，才建造出了达到国际水准的美式洋楼。德胜力图以一己之力，培养具有平民意识的现代公民，德胜使得过去的农民蜕变为真正的产业工人和现代社会公民。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The employee manual of Tecsun (Suzhou) Homes Co., Ltd. has been a focus in the business management for years. Tecsun Homes is a small-scaled ordinary residence building company that constructs wooden/steel frame structured houses, unique in its staff management and remolding. The employee manual of Tecsun Homes institutionalized all the matters we might come across in operating a company. The corporation is totally system-based in its business management, and any affairs in working place can be dealt according to certain rule or regulation. Those rules and regulations reflecting the management philosophy of Tecsun Homes are plainly wording, and it has been internalized in each employee. By doing so, Tecsun Homes is meant to remold those migrant workers into decent industrial workers. In Tecsun Homes, any hard-working man can live a comfortable life with dignity, with welfare, yet with no worry about food and clothing. To ensure its quality, any work must be done by following its established procedures in Tecsun Homes. It is their stubborn attachment to those procedures that makes it possible for Tecsun Homes to build world-class Western-style buildings. Single-handedly, Tecsun Homes makes great effort to cultivate modern citizen with civilian consciousness. Tecsun Homes has successfully reshaped local peasants into real industrial workers, and qualified modern citizen as well.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2013</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业社会责任与商业伦理》、《人力资源管理》、《质量管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业社会责任理论、利益相关者理论、企业公民理论、制度化管理与细节管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2014-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
